testsuite.class: Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological

testcase.class: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0018. If waitOnParentSuccess is true in the pipelines configuration section, the pipeline will not run while a parent is incomplete.
testcase.classclass: P_WF_0018. If waitOnParentSuccess is true in the pipelines configuration section, the pipeline will not run while a parent is incomplete.

testcase.class: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0019. If waitOnParentComplete is true in the pipelines configuration section, no new run is created for additional pipeline triggers with the same steps.
testcase.classclass: P_WF_0019. If waitOnParentComplete is true in the pipelines configuration section, no new run is created for additional pipeline triggers with the same steps.

testcase.class: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0020. If waitOnParentComplete is true in the pipelines configuration section, a new run is created for additional pipeline triggers with different steps.
testcase.classclass: P_WF_0020. If waitOnParentComplete is true in the pipelines configuration section, a new run is created for additional pipeline triggers with different steps.

testcase.class: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0021. If waitOnParentComplete and chronological are true in the pipelines configuration section, the pipeline will not run until the parent is complete and one run at a time.
testcase.classclass: P_WF_0021. If waitOnParentComplete and chronological are true in the pipelines configuration section, the pipeline will not run until the parent is complete and one run at a time.

testcase.class: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for pipeline dependencyMode and chronological P_WF_0022. If waitOnParentComplete and waitOnChildComplete are both true, it waits for both.
testcase.classclass: P_WF_0022. If waitOnParentComplete and waitOnChildComplete are both true, it waits for both.
